{"content":[{"id":"31760216","settings":{"layout":"full_width","premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom","background_background":"classic","background_color":"#0D5286","background_image":{"url":"https:\/\/engineeringmanagementinstitute.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/unspecified-5-1-e1725289591609.jpg","id":65446,"size":"","alt":"","source":"library"},"background_attachment":"fixed","padding":{"unit":"px","top":"15","right":"15","bottom":"15","left":"15","isLinked":true},"pa_condition_repeater":[],"background_size":"cover","background_overlay_background":"classic","background_overlay_color":"#3A3A3A","background_overlay_opacity":{"unit":"px","size":0.8,"sizes":[]},"background_position_tablet":"center center","background_repeat_tablet":"no-repeat","background_size_tablet":"cover","background_size_mobile":"cover"},"elements":[{"id":"29786fdf","settings":{"_column_size":100,"_inline_size":100,"pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom"},"elements":[{"id":"7884b3b0","settings":{"editor":"<h2 data-elementor-setting-key=\"title\" data-pen-placeholder=\"Type Here...\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 40px; font-style: italic; letter-spacing: 5.2px; mix-blend-mode: screen; text-align: center;\">Meet Anthony Fasano, PE, AEC PM, F. ASCE<\/h2><h2 data-elementor-setting-key=\"title\" data-pen-placeholder=\"Type Here...\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 40px; font-style: italic; letter-spacing: 5.2px; mix-blend-mode: screen; text-align: center;\">(EMI's Founder)<\/h2>","pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom"},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"},{"id":"58806de6","settings":{"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom","structure":"20","pa_condition_repeater":[]},"elements":[{"id":"5ced04c3","settings":{"_column_size":50,"_inline_size":null,"pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom"},"elements":[{"id":"359516d8","settings":{"editor":"<p>Like many engineers, I had a goal of becoming a high-level executive in my engineering organization.\u00a0 When observing the leaders in my company, it was obvious that they possessed skills in addition to their technical skills, namely great people management or \u2018soft\u2019 skills.\u00a0 So, I set out to develop my \u2018soft skills,\u2019 a move that not only rapidly advanced my career, but led to me becoming an internal coach and trainer for my company, and ultimately inspired me to leave my engineering career behind to spend more time helping engineers become more effective managers and leaders.<\/p>","text_color":"#FFFFFF","typography_typography":"custom","typography_font_size":{"unit":"px","size":23,"sizes":[]},"pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom","_background_background":"classic","typography_font_family":"Montserrat"},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"}],"isInner":true,"elType":"column"},{"id":"50848b1d","settings":{"_column_size":50,"_inline_size":null,"pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom"},"elements":[{"id":"777e9b62","settings":{"image":{"url":"https:\/\/engineeringmanagementinstitute.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/Origin-Story.jpg","id":65741,"size":"","alt":"About Anthony Fasano","source":"library"},"pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom"},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"image","elType":"widget"}],"isInner":true,"elType":"column"}],"isInner":true,"elType":"section"},{"id":"1d6e36d0","settings":{"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom","pa_condition_repeater":[]},"elements":[{"id":"2575af87","settings":{"_column_size":100,"_inline_size":null,"pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom"},"elements":[{"id":"ceb7d61","settings":{"editor":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">When I first decided to try to help engineers develop their management skills on a broad scale, people told me I wouldn\u2019t succeed.\u00a0 They said engineers aren\u2019t interested in developing these skills and they certainly wouldn\u2019t listen to podcasts or watch videos on the subject.\u00a0 Well, three million downloads later and a Forbes citation has proven them wrong.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Engineers with sound people and project management skills can accomplish anything, for themselves and their firms, and our mission is to make sure that sustainable engineering management learning opportunities are available to every organization and engineer who needs them.<\/span><\/p><p><strong>Let us help you succeed.<\/strong><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><em>Anthony Fasano, PE<\/em><br \/><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Author of Engineer Your Own Success<br \/><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">President &amp; CEO - Engineering Management Institute<\/span><\/p>","text_color":"#FFFFFF","pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom","_background_background":"classic","typography_typography":"custom","typography_font_family":"Montserrat","typography_font_size":{"unit":"px","size":23,"sizes":[]}},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"},{"id":"50d0d1ae","settings":{"content_width":"full","text":"EMI's Mission, Vision, and Values","align":"center","button_text_color":"#202020","background_color":"#E7A60E","border_border":"solid","bo